{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.202604170002","title":"Ide yang tidak ditulis sama dengan ide yang tidak ada","desc":"Gagasan yang hanya ada di kepala bersifat sementara dan tidak bisa dikombinasikan dengan gagasan lain","tags":["zettel","knowledge-management","writing"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.202604170002","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"769b921393a5171c4e31739a1d647010","updated":1776683200139,"created":1776683200139,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170002","id":"zettel.202604170002","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.zettel","alias":"zettel","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.zettel"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170002","id":"zettel.202604170002","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.knowledge-management","alias":"knowledge-management","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.knowledge-management"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170002","id":"zettel.202604170002","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.writing","alias":"writing","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.writing"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170002","id":"zettel.202604170002","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.202604170001","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":17,"offset":1111},"end":{"line":24,"column":40,"offset":1134},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.202604170001"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170002","id":"zettel.202604170002","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.202604170003","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":20,"offset":1279},"end":{"line":25,"column":43,"offset":1302},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.202604170003"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170002","id":"zettel.202604170002","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":3,"offset":1412},"end":{"line":29,"column":48,"offset":1457},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":98,"column":3,"offset":8431},"end":{"line":98,"column":26,"offset":8454},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170002"},{"from":{"fname":"notes.zettelkasten","id":"notes.zettelkasten","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":110,"column":3,"offset":4017},"end":{"line":110,"column":26,"offset":4040},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170002"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170001","id":"zettel.202604170001","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":13,"offset":948},"end":{"line":21,"column":36,"offset":971},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170002"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.202604170003","id":"zettel.202604170003","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":18,"offset":1322},"end":{"line":24,"column":41,"offset":1345},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170002"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain","id":"zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":18,"offset":1268},"end":{"line":30,"column":41,"offset":1291},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170002"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain","id":"zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":47,"column":3,"offset":1953},"end":{"line":47,"column":26,"offset":1976},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170002"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management","id":"zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":863},"end":{"line":22,"column":26,"offset":886},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170002"}],"anchors":{"gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Gagasan","value":"gagasan","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Ini Penting","value":"mengapa-ini-penting","line":25,"column":0,"depth":2},"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain":{"type":"header","text":"Hubungan ke Zettel Lain","value":"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain","line":34,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":39,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"ide-yang-tidak-ditulis-sama-dengan-ide-yang-tidak-ada\">Ide yang tidak ditulis sama dengan ide yang tidak ada<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#ide-yang-tidak-ditulis-sama-dengan-ide-yang-tidak-ada\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"gagasan\">Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Sebuah ide yang hanya hidup di kepala memiliki dua kelemahan fatal:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Tidak persisten</strong> — bisa hilang kapan saja, terutama saat tidur, distraksi, atau waktu berlalu</li>\n<li><strong>Tidak bisa dikombinasikan</strong> — ide di kepala tidak bisa <em>bertemu</em> dengan ide lain yang juga ada di kepala, tidak seperti dua catatan tertulis yang bisa dibaca bersama dan dibandingkan</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Menulis bukan hanya merekam — menulis adalah <strong>eksternalisasi gagasan</strong> sehingga bisa diperiksa, diperbaiki, dan dihubungkan.</p>\n<p>Luhmann sendiri bilang: <em>\"We should reflect on whether and how we arrange our notes so that they are available for later access.\"</em> Kata kunci: <em>available for later access</em> — ide yang tidak ditulis tidak tersedia untuk akses berikutnya.</p>\n<h2 id=\"mengapa-ini-penting\">Mengapa Ini Penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Banyak orang merasa sudah \"tahu\" sesuatu karena pernah membacanya. Tapi tanpa menuliskannya, pengetahuan itu tidak bisa:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dikritik dan disempurnakan</li>\n<li>Dihubungkan ke pengetahuan lain</li>\n<li>Digunakan saat insight itu relevan di masa depan</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Mengandalkan memori saja = <em>Collector's Fallacy</em> dalam bentuk digital.</p>\n<h2 id=\"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\">Hubungan ke Zettel Lain<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Didasari oleh <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170001\">Second brain memperluas kapasitas berpikir dengan memindahkan beban memori ke sistem eksternal</a> — karena otak yang tidak bisa diandalkan untuk menyimpan adalah <em>alasan</em> mengapa menulis wajib dilakukan setiap kali ada ide</li>\n<li>Mengimplikasikan <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170003\">Koneksi antar gagasan lebih bernilai dari koleksi informasi</a> — karena ketika ide ditulis, barulah ia bisa <em>terhubung</em> dengan ide lain dan menciptakan nilai</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain\">Literature Note — Building a Second Brain</a> — Bab 3 tentang \"Collector's Fallacy\"</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zettelkasten.de/introduction/\">Introduction to the Zettelkasten Method</a> — bagian \"The Body of the Zettel\"</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #a03623;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettel\">zettel</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #75bbfd;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.writing\">writing</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/notes.zettelkasten\">Zettelkasten di Dendron — Panduan Implementasi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170001\">Second brain memperluas kapasitas berpikir dengan memindahkan beban memori ke sistem eksternal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170003\">Koneksi antar gagasan lebih bernilai dari koleksi informasi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain\">Literature Note — Building a Second Brain</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management\">MOC: Personal Knowledge Management</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"seeds":{"dendron.templates":{}},"enableFullHierarchyNoteTitle":false},"preview":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enableFrontmatterTags":true,"enableHashesForFMTags":false,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableKatex":true,"automaticallyShowPreview":false},"publishing":{"enableFMTitle":true,"enableNoteTitleForLink":true,"enablePrettyRefs":true,"enableKatex":true,"copyAssets":true,"siteHierarchies":["root"],"writeStubs":